data.description: ** No City Taxes! ** Enjoy the open concept living/kitchen area with downstairs primary suite, and bonus room perfect for a home office, homeschool, gym, or playroom. The kitchen features gas range, granite countertops, stainless appliances, and a breakfast bar. Large 2nd Living area upstairs. Enjoy coffee and cookouts under the shade of the covered patio.  Amenities abound with a pool, sports courts, park/playground, and clubhouse. Conveniently located near IH10, HWY 78, & 1604 & only 12 miles to the Forum Shopping Center, 20 min to downtown San Antonio, Live Oak, and Toyota!
